msgid ""
"Proper DNS configuration is essential for email deliverability. Configure "
"SPF, DKIM, and DMARC records to ensure your emails reach recipients' inboxes "
"instead of spam folders."
msgstr ""
"Eine korrekte DNS-Konfiguration ist für die E-Mail-Übermittlung "
