"möchten."

msgid "Domestic Services (Canada)"
msgstr "Inländliche Dienstleistungen (Kanada)"

msgid "Service Code"
msgstr "Dienstcode"

msgid "Service Name"
msgstr "Dienstname"

msgid "Standard ground delivery (2-9 business days)"
msgstr "Standard-Flächenversand (2–9 Werktagen)"

msgid "Expedited Parcel"
msgstr "Beschleunigtes Paket"

msgid "Faster ground service (1-7 business days)"
msgstr "Schnellerer Flächenversand (1–7 Werktagen)"

msgid "Xpresspost"
msgstr "Xpresspost"

msgid "Next-day to 2-day delivery with tracking"
msgstr "Lieferung am nächsten Tag bis zu 2 Tage mit Tracking"

msgid "Priority"
msgstr "Priorität"

msgid "Overnight to most Canadian destinations"
msgstr "Übernachtung zu den meisten kanadischen Zielorten"

msgid "USA Services"
msgstr "USA-Dienste"

msgid "Expedited Parcel USA"
msgstr "Express-Paket USA"

msgid "Ground service to USA (4-7 business days)"
msgstr "Flächenversand nach USA (4–7 Werktagen)"

msgid "Xpresspost USA"
msgstr "Xpresspost USA"

msgid "Fast air service to USA (2-3 business days)"
msgstr "Schneller Luftversand nach USA (2–3 Werktagen)"

msgid "Xpresspost International"
msgstr "Xpresspost International"

msgid "Fast air service to 65+ countries (4-7 business days)"
msgstr "Schneller Luftversand zu 65+ Ländern (4–7 Werktagen)"

msgid "International Parcel Air"
msgstr "Internationaler Luftversand"

msgid "Air service to worldwide destinations (6-12 business days)"
msgstr "Luftversand zu weltweiten Zielorten (6–12 Werktagen)"

msgid "International Parcel Surface"
msgstr "Internationaler Oberflächenversand"

msgid "Surface service (4-12 weeks, varies by destination)"
msgstr "Flächenversand (4–12 Wochen, variiert je nach Zielort)"

msgid ""
"All services are available to both Contract and Non-Contract customers, but "
"Contract customers receive discounted rates."
msgstr ""
"Alle Dienste sind sowohl für Vertrags- als auch für Nicht-Vertragskunden "
"verfügbar, Vertragskunden erhalten jedoch vergünstigte Preise."

msgid "Configure Shipping Options"
msgstr "Versandoptionen konfigurieren"

msgid ""
"Canada Post offers various shipping options that can be added to shipments."
msgstr ""
"Canada Post bietet verschiedene Versandoptionen, die zu Sendungen "
"hinzugefügt werden können."

msgid "Option Code"
msgstr "Option-Code"

msgid "Option Name"
msgstr "Option-Name"

msgid "Value Required"
msgstr "Wert erforderlich"

msgid "Signature"
msgstr "Signatur"

msgid "Signature required on delivery"
msgstr "Unterschrift bei der Lieferung erforderlich"

msgid "Coverage (Insurance)"
msgstr "Deckung (Versicherung)"

